{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_01.gif?t=1738074834\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The current demo contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fully redesigned low-poly graphics</strong> for a modern visual experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play as Ardan</strong>, an Aran\u2019thal archmage with powerful mage abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Edgescar Survival Map</strong>: Explore the grassland biome in our first survival map, playable up to day 6.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Nightly Undead Invasions</strong>: Face increasing challenges each night, culminating in a final demonic invasion for those who survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Orc Raids</strong>: Expand carefully, orc attacks intensify if you grow too quickly, adding strategic depth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dark Pylon Waves</strong>: Be proactive by destroying dark pylons before they unleash more enemy waves.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_04.gif?t=1738074834\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ardan\u2019s Class-Specific Quest</strong>: Embark on a unique quest line tailored for Ardan in the survival map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Improved AI</strong>: Experience smarter enemies that invade in formations for more engaging battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival Map Exploration</strong>: Delve into the survival map to find <strong>treasure chests</strong>, some locked, others requiring resource sacrifices to demons. Discover <strong>healing fountains</strong> to rest before the next battle.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_03.gif?t=1738074834\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>New Continent Map</strong>: Discover a brand-new world map used in the survival mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Scenario Editor</strong>: Create custom maps, script triggers, and design quests. Share your creations with others on the Steam Workshop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Darfall Wiki</strong>: Dive into the history, characters, and lore of the Darfall universe through our comprehensive wiki.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_02.gif?t=1738074834\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738074834","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/page.bg.jpg?t=1738074834","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/53d4376be702534588a7fa5d4861d542b00a5454/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738074834","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/53d4376be702534588a7fa5d4861d542b00a5454/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738074834","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085150/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_01.gif?t=1738074834\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The current demo contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fully redesigned low-poly graphics</strong> for a modern visual experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play as Ardan</strong>, an Aran\u2019thal archmage with powerful mage abilities.</p></li><l